Sentencas: Strontium doped lanthanum chromium manganite (LSCM) is a potential ceramic anode material for next-generation hydrocarbon-fueled solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Effect of Samaria Doped Ceria Impregnation on the Electrochemical Performance of Strontium Doped Lanthanum Chromium Manganite Anode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Because of its relatively low electrochemical performance, however, its application is still limited.
Titulo: Effect of Samaria Doped Ceria Impregnation on the Electrochemical Performance of Strontium Doped Lanthanum Chromium Manganite Anode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: This work investigated the effect of samaria-doped ceria (SDC) impregnation on the electrode performance regarding the surface reaction and oxygen-ion transport in the electrode reaction.
Titulo: Effect of Samaria Doped Ceria Impregnation on the Electrochemical Performance of Strontium Doped Lanthanum Chromium Manganite Anode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The results showed that the electrochemical performance had been promoted by incorporating with nano-SDC particles.
Titulo: Effect of Samaria Doped Ceria Impregnation on the Electrochemical Performance of Strontium Doped Lanthanum Chromium Manganite Anode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Electrical conductivity relaxation (ECR) of dense LSCM exhibited significant improvement in the surface exchange coefficient, from 5.34 x 10(-6) cm s(-1) at 850 degrees C for bare LSCM to 1.48 x 10(-4) cm s(-1) for LSCM coated with 0.9 mol L-1 SDC precursor solution.
Titulo: Effect of Samaria Doped Ceria Impregnation on the Electrochemical Performance of Strontium Doped Lanthanum Chromium Manganite Anode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The surface reaction promotion factor was about 28 for the nano SDC particle coating, much higher than the factor of 6.5 for LSCM-SDC composite.
Titulo: Effect of Samaria Doped Ceria Impregnation on the Electrochemical Performance of Strontium Doped Lanthanum Chromium Manganite Anode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: It was demonstrated that the promotion in surface reaction rate are mainly contributed by LSCM-SDC-gas three-phase boundaries (3PB).
Titulo: Effect of Samaria Doped Ceria Impregnation on the Electrochemical Performance of Strontium Doped Lanthanum Chromium Manganite Anode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Interfacial polarization resistances of SDC impregnated LSCM symmetrical cells presented over 1 order of magnitude reduction at 850 degrees C with a SDC loading of 35.8 wt%.
Titulo: Effect of Samaria Doped Ceria Impregnation on the Electrochemical Performance of Strontium Doped Lanthanum Chromium Manganite Anode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The electrode performance improvement was attributed to the connective oxygen ion conduction path and increased 3PB formed by the impregnated SDC particles.
Titulo: Effect of Samaria Doped Ceria Impregnation on the Electrochemical Performance of Strontium Doped Lanthanum Chromium Manganite Anode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
